Tentu saja dia hidup!

00:15:21.440 --> 00:15:22.580
Itu rumit.

00:15:43.080 --> 00:15:43.650
Ambil ini.

00:15:57.080 --> 00:15:57.650
Nona Bai,

00:15:57.960 --> 00:15:58.650
