Tidak ada apa-apa.

00:16:32.390 --> 00:16:33.460
Dia hanya tertidur.

00:16:34.080 --> 00:16:34.700
Guru Kedua Tu,

00:16:34.750 --> 00:16:35.340
Ayo pergi.

00:16:42.360 --> 00:16:42.980
Merindukan!

00:16:51.270 --> 00:16:51.850
Tunggu!

00:16:58.480 --> 00:16:59.980
Bagaimana penyakit anak saya?

